'''''Enterprise Magazine''''' launched in 1998 as ''Small Business Canada Magazine''. The name change to ''Enterprise'' was made in January 2005 as its readership grew to include small and medium-sized enterprises ([[Small and medium enterprises|SMEs]]) across Canada.

Based in [[Barrie]], [[Ontario]], ''Enterprise'' is published four times a year.<ref name="ssr"/> It is owned by Typgrafika Inc of Barrie, Ontario.<ref name="ssr"/> The publisher is Hayden R. Bradshaw.<ref name="ssr">{{cite news|title=Magazines|url=http://www.sources.com/SSR/Docs/MNN2009-8h-Magazines.pdf|accessdate=27 March 2017|work=SSR|date=2009}}</ref>

